"The Inverse Distance to a Power gridding method is a weighted average "
"interpolator."
msgstr ""
"Metod mreže inverznog rastojanja na stepen je interpolator ponderisanog "
"proseka."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:768
msgid ""
"You should supply the input arrays with the scattered data values including "
"coordinates of every data point and output grid geometry. The function will "
"compute interpolated value for the given position in output grid."
msgstr ""
"Treba da zadate ulazne nizove sa rasejanim vrednostima podataka, uključujući"
" koordinate svake tačke podataka, i geometriju izlazne mreže. Funkcija će "
"izračunati interpoliranu vrednost za zadatu poziciju u izlaznoj mreži."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:805
msgid "**Smothing**"
msgstr "**Zaglađivanje**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:853
