msgid "**Interpolated (IDW)**"
msgstr "**Interpolirano (IDW)**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:938
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``gdal:gridinversedistance``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``gdal:gridinversedistance``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:948
msgid "Grid (Linear)"
msgstr "Mreža (linearna)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:949
msgid ""
"The Linear method perform linear interpolation by computing a Delaunay "
"triangulation of the point cloud, finding in which triangle of the "
"triangulation the point is, and by doing linear interpolation from its "
"barycentric coordinates within the triangle. If the point is not in any "
"triangle, depending on the radius, the algorithm will use the value of the "
"nearest point or the NoData value."
msgstr ""
"Linearni metod vrši linearnu interpolaciju tako što računa Delonijevu "
"triangulaciju oblaka tačaka, pronalazi u kom trouglu triangulacije se tačka "
"nalazi i vrši linearnu interpolaciju iz njenih baricentričnih koordinata "
"unutar trougla. Ako tačka nije ni u jednom trouglu, u zavisnosti od "
"poluprečnika, algoritam će koristiti vrednost najbliže tačke ili NoData "
"vrednost."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:978
msgid "**Search distance**"
msgstr "**Rastojanje pretrage**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:982
msgid "Default: -1.0"
msgstr "Podrazumevano: -1.0"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:983
msgid ""
"In case the point to be interpolated does not fit into a triangle of the "
"Delaunay triangulation, use that maximum distance to search a nearest "
"neighbour, or use NoData otherwise. If set to ``-1``, the search distance is"
" infinite. If set to ``0``, NoData value will be used."
msgstr ""
"U slučaju da tačka koja se interpolira ne staje u trougao Delonijeve "
"triangulacije, koristi to maksimalno rastojanje za pretragu najbližeg "
"suseda, ili u suprotnom koristi NoData. Ako je postavljeno na ``-1``, "
"rastojanje pretrage je beskonačno. Ako je postavljeno na ``0``, koristiće se"
" NoData vrednost."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:995
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1072
msgid "**Interpolated (Linear)**"
msgstr "**Interpolirano (linearno)**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1080
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``gdal:gridlinear``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``gdal:gridlinear``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1090
msgid "Grid (Moving average)"
msgstr "Mreža (pokretni prosek)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1091
msgid ""
"The Moving Average is a simple data averaging algorithm. It uses a moving "
"window of elliptic form to search values and averages all data points within"
" the window. Search ellipse can be rotated by specified angle, the center of"
" ellipse located at the grid node. Also the minimum number of data points to"
" average can be set, if there are not enough points in window, the grid node"
" considered empty and will be filled with specified NoData value."
msgstr ""
"Pokretni prosek je jednostavan algoritam usrednjavanja podataka. Koristi "
"pokretni prozor eliptičnog oblika za pretragu vrednosti i usrednjava sve "
"tačke podataka unutar prozora. Pretražna elipsa se može rotirati za zadati "
"ugao, centar elipse nalazi se u čvoru mreže. Takođe se može postaviti "
"minimalni broj tačaka podataka za usrednjavanje; ako u prozoru nema dovoljno"
" tačaka, čvor mreže se smatra praznim i biće popunjen zadatom NoData "
"vrednošću."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1162
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1238
msgid "**Interpolated (moving average)**"
msgstr "**Interpolirano (pokretni prosek)**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1167
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1633
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1796
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1929
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:2054
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:2176
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:2296
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:2408
msgid ""
"Specify the output raster layer. :ref:`One of <output_parameter_widget>`:"
msgstr ""
"Zadajte izlazni rasterski sloj. :ref:`Jedno od <output_parameter_widget>`:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1246
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``gdal:gridaverage``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``gdal:gridaverage``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1256
msgid "Grid (Nearest neighbor)"
msgstr "Mreža (najbliži sused)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1257
msgid ""
"The Nearest Neighbor method doesn't perform any interpolation or smoothing, "
"it just takes the value of nearest point found in grid node search ellipse "
"and returns it as a result. If there are no points found, the specified "
"NoData value will be returned."
msgstr ""
"Metod najbližeg suseda ne vrši nikakvu interpolaciju ili zaglađivanje, već "
"samo uzima vrednost najbliže tačke pronađene u pretražnoj elipsi čvora mreže"
" i vraća je kao rezultat. Ako se ne pronađe nijedna tačka, vratiće se zadata"
" NoData vrednost."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1316
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1393
msgid "**Interpolated (Nearest neighbour)**"
msgstr "**Interpolirano (najbliži sused)**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1401
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``gdal:gridnearestneighbor``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``gdal:gridnearestneighbor``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1411
msgid "Hillshade"
msgstr "Osenčeni reljef"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1412
msgid ""
"Outputs a raster with a nice shaded relief effect. It’s very useful for "
"visualizing the terrain. You can optionally specify the azimuth and altitude"
" of the light source, a vertical exaggeration factor and a scaling factor to"
" account for differences between vertical and horizontal units."
msgstr ""
"Daje raster sa lepim efektom osenčenog reljefa. Veoma je koristan za "
"vizuelizaciju terena. Opciono možete zadati azimut i visinu izvora "
"svetlosti, faktor vertikalnog preuveličavanja i faktor skaliranja radi "
"uzimanja u obzir razlika između vertikalnih i horizontalnih jedinica."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1418
msgid ""
"This algorithm is derived from the `GDAL DEM utility "
"<https://gdal.org/en/latest/programs/gdaldem.html>`__ ."
msgstr ""
"Ovaj algoritam je izveden iz `GDAL DEM alatke "
"<https://gdal.org/en/latest/programs/gdaldem.html>`__ ."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1441
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1612
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1735
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:2140
