msgstr "Ulazni rasterski sloj nadmorskih visina"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1447
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1741
