msgstr "Faktor preuveličava visinu izlaznog visinskog rastera"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1455
msgid "**Scale (ratio of vertical units to horizontal)**"
msgstr "**Razmera (odnos vertikalnih i horizontalnih jedinica)**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1456
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:2148
msgid "``SCALE``"
msgstr "``SCALE``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1460
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:2152
msgid "The ratio of vertical units to horizontal units"
msgstr "Odnos vertikalnih i horizontalnih jedinica"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1461
msgid "**Azimuth of the light**"
msgstr "**Azimut svetlosti**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1462
msgid "``AZIMUTH``"
msgstr "``AZIMUTH``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1465
msgid "Default: 315.0"
msgstr "Podrazumevano: 315.0"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1466
msgid ""
"Defines the azimuth of the light shining on the elevation raster in degrees."
" If it comes from the top of the raster the value is 0, if it comes from the"
" east it is 90 a.s.o."
msgstr ""
"Definiše azimut svetlosti koja obasjava visinski raster u stepenima. Ako "
"dolazi sa vrha rastera vrednost je 0, ako dolazi sa istoka 90 itd."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1470
msgid "**Altitude of the light**"
msgstr "**Visina svetlosti**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1471
msgid "``ALTITUDE``"
msgstr "``ALTITUDE``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1474
msgid "Default: 45.0"
msgstr "Podrazumevano: 45.0"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1475
msgid ""
"Defines the altitude of the light, in degrees. 90 if the light comes from "
"above the elevation raster, 0 if it is raking light."
msgstr ""
"Definiše visinu svetlosti u stepenima. 90 ako svetlost dolazi iznad "
"visinskog rastera, 0 ako je svetlost pod oštrim uglom."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1484
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:2165
msgid "**Use Zevenbergen&Thorne formula (instead of the Horn's one)**"
msgstr "**Koristi Zevenbergen&Thorne formulu (umesto Hornove)**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1490
msgid "**Combined shading**"
msgstr "**Kombinovano senčenje**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1491
msgid "``COMBINED``"
msgstr "``COMBINED``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1496
msgid "**Multidirectional shading**"
msgstr "**Višesmerno senčenje**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1497
msgid "``MULTIDIRECTIONAL``"
msgstr "``MULTIDIRECTIONAL``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1502
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1562
msgid "**Hillshade**"
msgstr "**Osenčeni reljef**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1570
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``gdal:hillshade``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``gdal:hillshade``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1580
msgid "Near black"
msgstr "Skoro crno"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1581
msgid "Converts nearly black/white borders to black."
msgstr "Pretvara skoro crne/bele granice u crne."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1583
msgid ""
"This algorithm will scan an image and try to set all pixels that are nearly "
"or exactly black, white or one or more custom colors around the collar to "
"black or white. This is often used to \"fix up\" lossy compressed airphotos "
"so that color pixels can be treated as transparent when mosaicking."
msgstr ""
"Ovaj algoritam će skenirati sliku i pokušati da sve piksele koji su skoro "
"ili tačno crni, beli ili jedne ili više prilagođenih boja oko oboda postavi "
"na crne ili bele. Ovo se često koristi za „popravku“ aerofotografija sa "
"gubitkom kompresije, kako bi se obojeni pikseli mogli tretirati kao prozirni"
" pri pravljenju mozaika."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1589
msgid ""
"This algorithm is derived from the `GDAL nearblack utility "
"<https://gdal.org/en/latest/programs/nearblack.html>`_."
msgstr ""
"Ovaj algoritam je izveden iz `GDAL nearblack alatke "
"<https://gdal.org/en/latest/programs/nearblack.html>`_."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1613
msgid "**How far from black (white)**"
msgstr "**Koliko daleko od crne (bele)**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1614
msgid "``NEAR``"
msgstr "``NEAR``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1617
msgid "Default: 15"
msgstr "Podrazumevano: 15"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1618
msgid ""
"Select how far from black, white or custom colors the pixel values can be "
"and still considered near black, white or custom color."
msgstr ""
"Izaberite koliko daleko od crne, bele ili prilagođenih boja vrednosti "
"piksela mogu biti a da se i dalje smatraju skoro crnim, belim ili "
"prilagođene boje."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1621
msgid "**Search for nearly white pixels instead of nearly black**"
msgstr "**Traži skoro bele piksele umesto skoro crnih**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1622
msgid "``WHITE``"
msgstr "``WHITE``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1626
msgid "Search for nearly white (255) pixels instead of nearly black pixels"
msgstr "Traži skoro bele (255) piksele umesto skoro crnih piksela"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1628
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1687
msgid "**Nearblack**"
msgstr "**Skoro crno**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1695
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``gdal:nearblack``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``gdal:nearblack``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1705
msgid "Proximity (raster distance)"
msgstr "Blizina (rastojanje u rasteru)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1706
msgid ""
"Generates a raster proximity map indicating the distance from the center of "
"each pixel to the center of the nearest pixel identified as a target pixel. "
"Target pixels are those in the source raster for which the raster pixel "
"value is in the set of target pixel values."
msgstr ""
"Generiše rastersku kartu blizine koja označava rastojanje od centra svakog "
"piksela do centra najbližeg piksela označenog kao ciljni piksel. Ciljni "
"pikseli su oni u izvornom rasteru čija je vrednost piksela u skupu vrednosti"
" ciljnih piksela."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1712
msgid ""
"This algorithm is derived from the `GDAL proximity utility "
"<https://gdal.org/en/latest/programs/gdal_proximity.html>`_."
msgstr ""
"Ovaj algoritam je izveden iz `GDAL proximity alatke "
"<https://gdal.org/en/latest/programs/gdal_proximity.html>`_."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1742
msgid "**List of target pixels**"
msgstr "**Lista ciljnih piksela**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1745
msgid "``VALUES``"
msgstr "``VALUES``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1749
msgid ""
"Comma-separated list of pixel values in the source image to consider as "
"target pixels. If not specified, all non-zero pixels will be considered "
"target pixels."
msgstr ""
"Lista vrednosti piksela u izvornoj slici, razdvojenih zarezima, koji se "
"smatraju ciljnim pikselima. Ako nije zadata, svi pikseli različiti od nule "
"smatraće se ciljnim pikselima."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1751
msgid "**Distance units**"
msgstr "**Jedinice rastojanja**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1752
msgid "``UNITS``"
msgstr "``UNITS``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1756
msgid ""
"Indicate whether distances generated should be in pixel or georeferenced "
"coordinates. One of:"
msgstr ""
"Označava da li generisana rastojanja treba da budu u pikselskim ili "
"georeferenciranim koordinatama. Jedno od:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1759
msgid "0 --- Georeferenced coordinates"
msgstr "0 --- Georeferencirane koordinate"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1760
msgid "1 --- Pixel coordinates"
msgstr "1 --- Pikselske koordinate"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1762
msgid "**The maximum distance to generate**"
msgstr "**Maksimalno rastojanje koje se generiše**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1765
msgid "``MAX_DISTANCE``"
msgstr "``MAX_DISTANCE``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1769
msgid ""
"The maximum distance to be generated. The NoData value will be used for "
"pixels beyond this distance. Distance is interpreted according to the value "
"of the *Distance units* parameter."
msgstr ""
"Maksimalno rastojanje koje se generiše. NoData vrednost će se koristiti za "
"piksele izvan ovog rastojanja. Rastojanje se tumači prema vrednosti "
"parametra *Jedinice rastojanja*."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1772
msgid "**Value to apply to pixels within the maximum distance**"
msgstr ""
"**Vrednost koja se primenjuje na piksele unutar maksimalnog rastojanja**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1775
msgid "``REPLACE``"
msgstr "``REPLACE``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1779
msgid ""
"Specify a value to apply to all pixels that are within the maximum distance "
"from target pixels (including the target pixels) instead of a distance "
"value."
msgstr ""
"Zadajte vrednost koja se primenjuje na sve piksele koji su unutar "
"maksimalnog rastojanja od ciljnih piksela (uključujući ciljne piksele) "
"umesto vrednosti rastojanja."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1781
msgid "**NoData value to use for the destination proximity raster**"
msgstr "**NoData vrednost koja se koristi za odredišni raster blizine**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1788
msgid ""
"Specify the NoData value to use for the pixels beyond the maximum distance. "
"If a NoData value is not provided, the output band will be queried for its "
"NoData value. If the output band does not have a NoData value, then the "
"value ``65535`` will be used."
msgstr ""
"Zadajte NoData vrednost koja se koristi za piksele izvan maksimalnog "
"rastojanja. Ako NoData vrednost nije zadata, izlazni kanal će biti upitan za"
" svoju NoData vrednost. Ako izlazni kanal nema NoData vrednost, koristiće se"
" vrednost ``65535``."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1791
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1861
msgid "**Proximity map**"
msgstr "**Karta blizine**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1869
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``gdal:proximity``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``gdal:proximity``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1879
msgid "Roughness"
msgstr "Hrapavost"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1880
msgid ""
"Outputs a single-band raster with values computed from the elevation. "
"Roughness is the degree of irregularity of the surface. It's calculated by "
"the largest inter-cell difference of a central pixel and its surrounding "
"cell. The determination of the roughness plays a role in the analysis of "
"terrain elevation data, it's useful for calculations of the river "
"morphology, in climatology and physical geography in general."
msgstr ""
"Daje jednokanalni raster sa vrednostima izračunatim iz visine. Hrapavost je "
"stepen nepravilnosti površine. Računa se kao najveća razlika između "
"centralnog piksela i njegovih okolnih ćelija. Određivanje hrapavosti igra "
"ulogu u analizi visinskih podataka terena, korisno je za proračune "
"morfologije reka, u klimatologiji i fizičkoj geografiji uopšte."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1924
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1975
msgid "**Roughness**"
msgstr "**Hrapavost**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1978
msgid ""
"Single-band output roughness raster. The value -9999 is used as NoData "
"value."
msgstr ""
"Jednokanalni izlazni raster hrapavosti. Vrednost -9999 se koristi kao NoData"
" vrednost."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1984
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``gdal:roughness``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``gdal:roughness``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1994
msgid "Sieve"
msgstr "Prosej"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1995
msgid ""
"Removes raster polygons smaller than a provided threshold size (in pixels) "
"and replaces them with the pixel value of the largest neighbour polygon. It "
"is useful if you have a large amount of small areas on your raster map."
msgstr ""
"Uklanja rasterske poligone manje od zadate granične veličine (u pikselima) i"
" zamenjuje ih vrednošću piksela najvećeg susednog poligona. Korisno je ako "
"na rasterskoj karti imate veliki broj malih oblasti."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:1999
msgid ""
"This algorithm is derived from the `GDAL sieve utility "
"<https://gdal.org/en/latest/programs/gdal_sieve.html>`_."
msgstr ""
"Ovaj algoritam je izveden iz `GDAL sieve alatke "
"<https://gdal.org/en/latest/programs/gdal_sieve.html>`_."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:2023
msgid "**Threshold**"
msgstr "**Prag**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:2024
msgid "``THRESHOLD``"
msgstr "``THRESHOLD``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:2028
msgid "Only raster polygons smaller than this size will be removed"
msgstr "Uklanjaju se samo rasterski poligoni manji od ove veličine"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:2030
msgid "**Use 8-connectedness**"
msgstr "**Koristi 8-povezanost**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:2031
msgid "``EIGHT_CONNECTEDNESS``"
msgstr "``EIGHT_CONNECTEDNESS``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:2035
msgid ""
"If False, consider as neighbours only the (4) pixels that connect the edges "
"horizontally or vertically. If True, every pixel that touches an edge or a "
"corner is considered as neighbour."
msgstr ""
"Ako je False, kao susedi se smatraju samo (4) piksela koji povezuju ivice "
"horizontalno ili vertikalno. Ako je True, svaki piksel koji dodiruje ivicu "
"ili ugao smatra se susedom."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:2037
msgid "**Do not use the default validity mask for the input band**"
msgstr "**Ne koristi podrazumevanu masku ispravnosti za ulazni kanal**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:2038
msgid "``NO_MASK``"
msgstr "``NO_MASK``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:2048
msgid "Validity mask to use instead of the default"
msgstr "Maska ispravnosti koja se koristi umesto podrazumevane"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:2049
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:2093
msgid "**Sieved**"
msgstr "**Prosejano**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:2096
msgid "Output raster layer."
msgstr "Izlazni rasterski sloj."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:2101
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``gdal:sieve``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``gdal:sieve``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:2111
msgid "Slope"
msgstr "Nagib"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:2112
msgid ""
"Generates a slope map from any GDAL-supported elevation raster. Slope is the"
" angle of inclination to the horizontal. You have the option of specifying "
"the type of slope value you want: degrees or percent slope."
msgstr ""
"Generiše kartu nagiba iz bilo kog visinskog rastera koji GDAL podržava. "
"Nagib je ugao nagnutosti u odnosu na horizontalu. Imate mogućnost da zadate "
"tip vrednosti nagiba koji želite: nagib u stepenima ili u procentima."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:2147
msgid "**Ratio of vertical units to horizontal**"
msgstr "**Odnos vertikalnih i horizontalnih jedinica**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:2153
msgid "**Express slope as percent (instead of degrees)**"
msgstr "**Izrazi nagib u procentima (umesto u stepenima)**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:2154
msgid "``AS_PERCENT``"
msgstr "``AS_PERCENT``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:2158
msgid "Express slope as percent instead of degrees"
msgstr "Izrazi nagib u procentima umesto u stepenima"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:2171
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:2230
msgid "**Slope**"
msgstr "**Nagib**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:2238
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``gdal:slope``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``gdal:slope``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:2248
msgid "Terrain Ruggedness Index (TRI)"
msgstr "Indeks razuđenosti terena (TRI)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:2249
msgid ""
"Outputs a single-band raster with values computed from the elevation. TRI "
"stands for Terrain Ruggedness Index, which is defined as the mean difference"
" between a central pixel and its surrounding cells."
msgstr ""
"Daje jednokanalni raster sa vrednostima izračunatim iz visine. TRI je "
"skraćenica za Indeks razuđenosti terena, koji se definiše kao srednja "
"razlika između centralnog piksela i njegovih okolnih ćelija."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:2291
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:2342
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:2403
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:2454
msgid "**Terrain Ruggedness Index**"
msgstr "**Indeks razuđenosti terena**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:2345
msgid "Output ruggedness raster. The value -9999 is used as NoData value."
msgstr ""
"Izlazni raster razuđenosti. Vrednost -9999 se koristi kao NoData vrednost."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:2351
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``gdal:triterrainruggednessindex``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``gdal:triterrainruggednessindex``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:2361
msgid "Topographic Position Index (TPI)"
msgstr "Indeks topografskog položaja (TPI)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:2362
msgid ""
"Outputs a single-band raster with values computed from the elevation. TPI "
"stands for Topographic Position Index, which is defined as the difference "
"between a central pixel and the mean of its surrounding cells."
msgstr ""
"Daje jednokanalni raster sa vrednostima izračunatim iz visine. TPI je "
"skraćenica za Indeks topografskog položaja, koji se definiše kao razlika "
"između centralnog piksela i srednje vrednosti njegovih okolnih ćelija."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:2396
msgid "The number of the band to use for elevation values"
msgstr "Broj kanala koji se koristi za vrednosti visine"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:2457
msgid "Output raster."
msgstr "Izlazni raster."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/gdal/rasteranalysis.rst:2462
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``gdal:tpitopographicpositionindex``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``gdal:tpitopographicpositionindex``"
